title: 2016 Burton US Open CLIF Best Trick – Ayumu Nedefuji, Halfpipe
description: Ayumu Nedefuji’s Japan air is what it took to win the CLIF Raise the Bar Award . CLIF challenges athletes to “Raise the Bar” with awards for best throwback and most progressive tricks. Awarded in both halfpipe and slopestyle with a $10,000 total prize purse up for grabs.
